name: Crazy Jet Fighter Doodle
description:
Can you handle this crazy fast Jet Fighter game? It's not like the normal ones you played before, it's crazy fast.

Year is 1942 x 1982 , we are back to the war and also back to retro black and white style shooting games.

Sit back and relax with this non-competitive vertical scroll shooter.

See what kind of scores you can get.
